MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

93-529. Ricciardi v. Babcock & Wilcox Co.

Summit County, No. 15728. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Summit County. Upon consideration of the joint application to dismiss,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective April 14, 1994.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
